GET {{LLMApi_HostAddress}}/api/mock/orders/summary?shape=%7B%22orderSummary%22%3A%7B%22orderId%22%3A%22string%22%2C%22total%22%3A0.0%2C%22items%22%3A%5B%7B%22sku%22%3A%22string%22%2C%22qty%22%3A0%7D%5D%7D%7D
Accept: application/json

###


